Rex E. Schlaybaugh, Jr.

Public asset : 190,427 USDLinked companies :  Syntel, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. Rex E. Schlaybaugh, Jr., is Chairman at Sealine International Ltd.He is on the Board of Directors at The Oxford Investment Group, Inc., Metropolitan Affairs Coalition, and Detroit Economic Growth Corp.Mr. Schlaybaugh was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Dykema Gossett PLLC, Chairman by Michigan Chamber of Commerce, and Chairman-Trustee Board by Oakland University.He received his undergraduate degree from Albion College and a graduate degree from the University of Detroit Mercy.



